  "informal_statement": "If g is a right inverse of f (f(g(x)) = x for all x), then f is surjective.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Given any b, the witness a := g b satisfies f a = f (g b) = b by the right-inverse equation, so f is surjective.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem right_inverse_surjective (α β : Type) (f : α → β) (g : β → α) (h : Function.RightInverse g f) : Function.Surjective f",
